0x27396C75.name: GET_VEHICLE_HANDLING_INT

params.name: vehicle
params.description: The vehicle to obtain data for.

params.name: class_
params.description: The handling class to get. Only "CHandlingData" is supported at this time.

params.name: fieldName
params.description: The field name to get. These match the keys in `handling.meta`.

0x27396C75.description:
Returns the effective handling data of a vehicle as an integer value.
Example: `local modelFlags = GetVehicleHandlingInt(vehicle, 'CHandlingData', 'strModelFlags')`
